description: CivicMinding helps you get informed on, vote on, and discuss everything political: bills making their way through congress; people running for, or serving an elected office; important issues of the day; and more! All contributions are private and secure, and could help influence decision-making and public opinion.
exampleInteractions: Alexa, ask CivicMinding for the Democrat delegate count?
Alexa, ask CivicMinding who is leading in the race for President?
Alexa, ask CivicMinding what bills were introduced this week?
name: CivicMinding
